  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, AI developers, including those behind the ChatGPT, can gain valuable insights from this study.",
    "They can focus on refining their AI models to address certain limitations, particularly information credibility and algorithmic biases.",
    "This will enable them to create more dependable and ethically sound educational AI tools that are better suited to the unique demands of the academic contexts.",
    "Although this study sheds light on the impact of ChatGPT in academia, several limitations should be considered.",
    "First, the study sample focused on a specific developing small island, which may limit the generalizability of the findings to broader international contexts."
  ]
}